    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "description": {
      "content": "REST API exposed by the Ray head node (default port 8265) for submitting,\nlisting, inspecting, and stopping Ray jobs and retrieving job logs.\nOpen-source Ray clusters are typically unauthenticated; production\ndeployments rely on network controls or Anyscale-managed authentication.\n\n\nContact Support:\n Name: Ray Project",
